            <h3 data-uuid="21c360e486d0452180acd1025b41cdce">Part 2: Write an Analytical Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="fb1d6cf359b0405197fd20b99375efa9">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="78a9738f19624eed8048014d51f2af60">In the 1400s Europeans
                began exploring the world, searching for new lands and new trade routes.
                Christopher Columbusâ€™s voyages led to new exchanges between Europe, Africa, and
                the Americas. In the 1500s Spain established a large empire in the Americas.
                Soon, other European nations competed with Spain by starting colonies in the
                Americas.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="42c763e818954294bb7dd44bd2661922">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="6f7dfe7e4e8e410dbb228a1d4ec945b9">The Columbian Exchange introduced the people of
                Europe and the Americas to new plants, animals, and ideas. Write an analytical essay in
                which you discuss how encounters between different peoples changed the world.</p>
            <section class="module-close-dbi" data-uuid="5b103e04543f433987ef86ba45790379">
                <p data-uuid="fd435b05f6694155a1910b91d0ee5007">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose your essay.</p>
                <ol data-uuid="7906cc2565f14ea8bdc4f654abe776ee">
                    <li data-uuid="f3479396792045c99c403f41dceeb418">
                        Review your notes and sources before you start writing.
                    </li>
                    <li data-uuid="072b7f7a54b84d8db1062ff2ccbe0c5c">
                        Use at least <i>three</i> of the sources in Part 1, and develop the topic
                        with relevant, well-chosen text evidence from the documents.
                    </li>
                    <li data-uuid="d4346e222f14488593040ad9d0757276">
                        Cite specific text evidence from each of the sources in your
                        response.
                    </li>
                    <li data-uuid="da0e7be0852c4f719c4c2d5bf3f9da6e">
                        Plan your essay so that it includes an introduction, several body paragraphs, and a concluding paragraph.</li>
                    <li data-uuid="06686d05366b4a97b7bd7586fb40c36f">Organize your essay in a clear and logical way, and use relevant details to support your analysis.</li>
                    <li data-uuid="4fb12a26ee274e6d89e3a3e929c99dd8">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas&#160;and supports the information you present.<br />
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </section>
        </section>
